<taxonomicName id="2E6B30DB10448B476D37A896E0186A83" authority="Hudson" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Senecio" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="506" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aquaticus">
Senecio 
<normalizedToken id="7400E328DAFBCF750712D9083415254B" originalValue="aquáticus" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">aquaticus</normalizedToken>
Hudson
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="643FEA165DECDABFCD2A19294C4BF7CD" pageId="null" pageNumber="506" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="6447E354CA1078CA08316B2C0702C5C0" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Wasser-Kreuzkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="DE72283F3868A57749FD4CF1A25FBEEA" pageId="null" pageNumber="506" type="description">
<paragraph id="7D2763E7D4D846D00AAAE7DD9F5A88F4" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<emphasis id="58179783D7000B439D5C3158B42A8A5B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">S. erraticus</emphasis>
(Nr. 11c) durch folgende Merkmale: 15-60 cm hoch; 
<emphasis id="E41AEB524E4CC1DBE56D15E8ACF61550" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">
Winkel zwischen der Hauptachse und den Zweigen kleiner als 40°; 
<normalizedToken id="9108C3F173B2C66EC405473E5AEC799D" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="4447B69448DBA7EF6D6F4BACDB1E14DE" originalValue="gelbgrün" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">gelbgruen</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="49EC20C7C9B20351B4B4FBC08FB050A4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">
bei den andern Arten der Artengruppe 
<normalizedToken id="E9A05A91DA8CA9BCE346B11B1F3E1E4C" originalValue="dunkelgrün" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">dunkelgruen</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
), 
<emphasis id="87AFB41E6A748CEFE1BE07A7AF8FE8A5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">mit deutlich nach vorn gerichteten Abschnitten</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="1DEEB256F63A991B4E0538D559EE23B4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">
<normalizedToken id="E36647FBB65897939A61C67988C29B1F" originalValue="größte" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">groesste</normalizedToken>
Breite der Abschnitte meist am Grunde
</emphasis>
)
<emphasis id="2CDD1B3846DD72107842616F87496025" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">;</emphasis>
die den Stengel umfassenden Zipfel der obern 
<normalizedToken id="EBBA41C285D8B275A0C9B62F0D81C021" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="B3ED3FDFB9F4E74D845A0FDBFBA0FCF2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">
<normalizedToken id="DCB18112D05BA96389C89091C9BF98E1" originalValue="höchstens" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">hoechstens</normalizedToken>
2teilig; 
<normalizedToken id="2369F32DA5F45B404CDB13F2697AE7C6" originalValue="Köpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Koepfe</normalizedToken>
im Durchmesser 2
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="32FAE703DD945F69BB42AF3378B83F90" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">3 cm.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="9542DC10B9D36E9E06322826ADEA9276" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer und 
<normalizedToken id="DFA866C1CE73EB831E4DAB155751756D" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">frueher</normalizedToken>
Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5EE4F33322A98D72D6817D56A03E95A2" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">
<emphasis id="2162C0988AAE8050DA0768EE104B6828" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="03021398945F23B858AF23C361FA6F0E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">40:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="4803485A5FDEE7CAAC1D03105F4DC781" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Afzelius 1949), aus Norddeutschland (Reese 1951).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="68551F0F227462733FAAE231EC2CD4C9" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">
<emphasis id="E7B6582ADF2C9C00B40841FBC7C2C42A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, seltener montan. Feuchte bis nasse, 
<normalizedToken id="7A47779915DBBE4B8EDD4C25D714560E" originalValue="nährstoffreiche" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">naehrstoffreiche</normalizedToken>
, neutrale, humose, tonige 
<normalizedToken id="407D50B2C69AC5D8C5FA948CFC88D0F1" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="989ECEA82CE490AF1CDA2847991C42F6" originalValue="Gedüngte" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Geduengte</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="DF3347B302D5AACF9A8AB8D6D5773F2D" originalValue="Naßwiesen" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Nasswiesen</normalizedToken>
, Weiden, Flachmoore.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7B138B47F240847B553977ECBA2913DF" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">
<emphasis id="BCFEC60216A352C770038697EFB60F6F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="6DE048281819B7226EACB0C3B83EC9A5" originalValue="Westeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Westeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pfianze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="623735E374E56EC9F2768C5E55EC8F76" originalValue="Ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="0C402A8E0436B7588A40F9A29A73FF94" originalValue="Südschweden" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Suedschweden</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="D1C7E2CA9A28C9DF7F7C7043CD409E66" originalValue="Böhmen" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Boehmen</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="DDE61324FA3FCA4870DD7B7F6F3BA825" originalValue="Niederösterreich" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Niederoesterreich</normalizedToken>
, Lombardei, Westalpen. - Im Gebiet besonders im westlichen Teil, ziemlich selten (dringt kaum in die innern 
<normalizedToken id="41F2AB81F2CECCDF1AA34558A42AB047" originalValue="Alpentäler" pageId="null" pageNumber="506">Alpentaeler</normalizedToken>
ein).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
